x dr bekker was senior director of global safety for amgen overseeing all aspects of product safety worldwide and also served as senior director of clinical development and director of clinical development where he was responsible for programs in inflammation bone metabolism and neurology programs at all stages of development from preclinical to postmarketing while at amgen dr bekker led the development and facilitated the approvals of several amgen products including enbrel®and kineret®and contributed to the evaluation of inlicensing candidates for the company previous to his tenure at amgen dr bekker spent nearly seven years at procter  gamble pharmaceuticals where he played a key role in the clinical development of the osteoporosis drug actonel® dr bekker received his medical training in his native south africa and his phd in molecular biology from penn state university not who youre looking for find other petrus bekkers on spoke contact telephone email background report public records powered by digital info wwwchemocentryxcom na na na na na na resume edit career chemocentryx inc vice president medical and clinical affairs education edit add a degree— eg bachelors in business administration blogs by industry voices there are currently no blogs by industry voices achievements and recognition edit add an achievement andor recognition— eg man of the year forbes  notable links edit the links below are powered by bing search results click edit to customize videos edit add a videofrom youtube or vimeo executives  featured people at chemocentryx inc maureen howard vice president of research david goeddel member shearman gary chairman gary shearman chairman and managing director hbm advisors juan jaen senior vice president drug discovery thomas schall president and ceo markus cappel senior vice president corporate and business development j wright senior vice president medicinal chemistry and preclinical development penglie zhang created on jun   by spoke   edited on ju